**The Next Commerce JS SDK emits 34 internal events that you can listen to for tracking and custom functionality.**

<Aside type="tip">
The SDK has two types of events: DOM events for SDK lifecycle and internal events for cart/checkout operations. Use `document.addEventListener` for DOM events and `next.on()` for internal events.
